  "description": "Boutique Chain showcase: OSTERIA's shore-system cultural acoustics through the full Boutique Chain at deep-immersion settings. Anomaly with TextureBlend 0.7 (maximum alternate texture layer) and ReverbSize 0.6 creates a large initial spatial context. Dissolving Archive at Chance 0.18 and Dissolve 0.55 — shore memories that dissolve at medium rate. Cathedral with DarkMix 0.80 and no BitCrush — the cathedral is clean but extremely dark, like a space deep below the shoreline. Submersion at maximum 8 stages and LFO 0.1 Hz for maximum all-pass phase rotation — the submersion envelope wraps everything in slow-moving phase water.",
